short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Jump to the right tab immediately, even when you have 100 tabs open.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Hotkey: Ctrl(Cmd)-Shift-Y.
